hotel_data.hotelier_welcome_message: Situated on the beautiful Kalafatis beach, right next to top centers and training schools for water sports, Aphrodite Beach Resort Mykonos is ideal for those adventure seekers. Spend your summer holidays here at Aphrodite Resort, where you will enjoy water skiing or windsurfing in Mykonos. At Kalafatis Beach, in Mykonos, Greece, the northern summer winds (known as “meltemia” in Greek) are very strong. In combination with the crystal clear azure waters and the ideal temperature for any water sports activity, including water skiing and scuba diving the marvelous seabed of Mykonos, a wonderful surfing experience from May to October is guarantee.

hotel_data.hotel_description: Aphrodite Beach Resort Hotel is situated next to the picturesque, blue-flag Kalafatis beach. It features a swimming pool, a tennis court, 3 restaurants and 3 bars. Wellness facilities include a fitness centre, sauna and 2 hot tubs. The Aphrodite Beach Resort Hotel offers stylish rooms with a balcony, most of them overlooking the Aegean Sea. All are well equipped with air conditioning, safety deposit box, satellite TV and mini fridge. Luxurious toiletries are also available. Guests may relax by the large swimming pool and enjoy a cocktail or snack at the pool bar. A variety of drinks and cocktails can also be enjoyed at the beach bar or at the champagne bar. The central restaurant and the beach-side "Thalassa" restaurant serve Greek & Mediterranean cuisine in an elegant setting, while gastronomic enthusiasts can taste creative dishes at the Blue Restaurant. Extra services include babysitting, laundry and ironing upon request. Massage treatments can also be arranged on request. Free, on-site parking is provided. The beach offers a number of activities, such as volleyball, windsurfing and scuba diving. Lively Mykonos Town is just a 15-minute drive. An on-site boutique is available at Aphrodite Beach Resort Hotel.

hotel_data.hotel_description: Margarita Studios is situated 200 metres from the sandy beach in the scenic fishing village of Abelas, just a 5-minute drive from the cosmopolitan Naoussa. It offers a swimming pool, a traditional restaurant and a hot tub. A flat-screen TV is included in all accommodation types at the Margarita Studios. Each unit comes with a private balcony. Air conditioning and marble bathrooms are provided. A playground and a children's pool are offered. Guests can relax on the sun terrace that features sun loungers and umbrellas. Explore your surroundings by renting a car. Take a stroll along the nearby beach or simply relax in the hot tub after a day of fun. In the evening, relax at the taverna and enjoy traditional home cooking and local wine.

“Margarita Studios” is a boutique hotel located right in the heart of the lovely traditional village of Ambelas, close to cosmopolitan Naoussa, surrounded by some of Paros most spectacular sandy beaches. The famous traditional houses of the island are completely renovated and transformed into deluxe rooms made for one, two or three quests, for families, into elegant suites and into stylish stone houses. History, luxury and tradition coexist, in order to serve our guests' needs.
Each material is carefully chosen and connected to the area, the people and their origin. All rooms feature modern amenities which offer warm hospitality and genuine personalised services. “Margarita Studios” was built having in mind both design and comfort.
 Drink your cocktail by the pool, enjoy the spectacular view of the Aegean Sea, relax with yoga, entertain yourself with zumba, take cooking lessons and impress your friends back home by making them a dinner using all the secrets of the Greek cuisine!
Margarita is not just a hotel. Margarita is the Greek friend that everyone would love to have. Margarita provides you with a different kind of holidays. More personal, more you!
